Package: openbullet2
Version: 2.0.1-0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: curl, tar, dotnet-sdk-10.0, npm, libsqlite
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/openbullet/OpenBullet2
Description: Cross-platform automation suite powered by .NET Core
 OpenBullet2 allows to perform requests towards a target webapp and offers
 many tools to work with the results. It can be used for scraping, parsing
 data, automated pentesting and much more.
